                <note rend="inline" type="source">819.001 Alfaro, Ricardo J./4: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Panama</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Davis</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-01-17T10:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 17, 1931—10 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 11:20 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>33. Department’s telegram No. 12, January 15, noon. Alfaro was inaugurated
                    yesterday at 4 p.m. I attended inauguration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Davis</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
